  "rationale": "<p>Substituting <em>x</em> = 2/5 into <em>f</em>(<em>x</em>) = 7(2/5 - <em>x</em>)<sup>2</sup> + 9/5 gives <em>f</em>(2/5) = 7(0)<sup>2</sup> + 9/5 = 9/5. As a decimal this equals 1.8. Either 9/5 or 1.8 is an acceptable answer.</p>",
